<div><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/emotional-ads-disgust-ad-2.png" alt="Emotional ads disgust ad" width="433" height="362" /></div>
</article>
</div>
<p>Click-through rate for the ad that provoked disgust was <strong>47% higher</strong> than the CTR for the above ad, which is boring and generic ‚Äì not eye-catching. The first ad commands attention.</p>
