</article>
</div>
<p>This ad was the clear winner of the three. <strong>Hitting users with the 1-2 punch of flattery <em>and</em> promotional details is key. </strong>We can still make the user feel good about themselves, while letting them know there‚Äôs a sale happening.</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="65af8c55-8eeb-4112-acf6-600631bb2d11" data-langcode="en">
